version_description: Thanks for using WeMesh!  Now you can enjoy meshing with your friends with Vimeo, Dropbox, and Google Drive integration, sing along with karaoke, and explore YouTube with our random video generator!  If you like WeMesh, don't forget to give us a rating!

Thanks for using WeMesh!  We're proud to bring you this update with bug fixes, performance improvements, and beautiful UI enhancements.  We hope you enjoy it, and are working on some (very) exciting new features to bring you soon.

Thanks for using WeMesh!  We're proud to bring you the biggest, best version of WeMesh yet, with full support for the iPad!  Stay tuned for future updates, amazing features on the way.

THE GLOBAL UPDATE

Thanks for using WeMesh! We love bringing people from all over the world together around the videos they love. With this update, you'll be able to see how international your mesh is, with a world map showing the approximate locations of all participants. Go global, and let the sun never set on your mesh!

We've also included bug fixes and performance improvements galore, to ensure this is the best WeMesh yet. Questions or comments? Email us at Support@WeMe.sh.

With this update, you'll be able to see how international your mesh is, with a world map showing the approximate locations of all participants. Go global, and let the sun never set on your mesh!

We've also included bug fixes and performance improvements galore, to ensure this is the best WeMesh yet. Questions or comments? Email us at Support@WeMe.sh.

THE RANDOM UPDATE

With this update, we're putting every one of the billion YouTube videos at your fingertips, waiting to be discovered.

Roll the dice for a Totally Random video - who knows what you'll find? Go where no one has gone before with Never Been Viewed, for videos with 0 views. Be the first to see a brand new video with Made This Minute, guaranteed to be less than 60 seconds old.

So grab some friends and dive deep into YouTube. And as always, thanks for using WeMesh.

We're excited to announce that WeMesh is now Rave. Rave will build upon WeMesh's strong foundation, to provide an even better experience.

This update is full of new features. A few key ones include the ability to minimize the video and vote while it plays (you'll understand when you try it), and rave settings! Now you can decide whether you want your rave to be vote driven or autoplay, turn on/off VoIP, and change the accessibility of the rave at any time. Rave your way.

Lastly, we want to thank all of our users. This is a big change, but rest assured it's the same app you love, better than ever. Big things are on the horizon, expect to hear about them very soon...
